<br>
Grim Fandango is kind of a latin 'Film noir' game where you work on a travel agency in the place where people go when they die before they move on to heaven or hell (The travel agency 'sells' tickets to heaven). You get involved in a murder and get thrown into an adventure full of gangsters, beatnicks and some GREAT music <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
